data.description:
This 3-year-old home sits on a spacious lot in a peaceful and highly sought-after neighborhood that just beams community in the great town of Mt Vernon,TX. Desirable school district. It's ideally situated close to the amenities of town without the feel of being too close. Only minutes away from Lake Cypress Springs, Lake Bob Sandlin, Sulphur Springs
This well-built modern farm-style home has an open floor plan, plenty of room to entertain guests, a covered rear patio that is a perfect place to sit & relax outdoors.Home features custom cabinetry, granite countertops throughout the kitchen and baths. A granite walk-in shower in owner's suite bathroom.
A one-year-old detached 8x12 outbuilding equipped with electricity, within Wi-Fi connectivity distance of the home. Currently serves as a home office. It would also make a great reading nook, art studio, hobby room, or – you name it!
Don't wait too long to schedule your viewing today. Tomorrow may be too late on this property!
